title: FRIDAY - Fantasy football Injury updates Week 8 2020
itunes:title: FRIDAY - Fantasy football Injury updates Week 8 2020
description:
Week 8 kicking off with a matchup between the Falcons and Panthers (0:07). Hear from Matt Ryan on Atlanta's mindset for the rest of the season (:40). We have the latest injury updates to help you set your fantasy lineups including the latest on Saints wide receiver Michael Thomas (1:34), Cowboys QB Andy Dalton (1:58) and Patriots wide receiver Julian Edelman (2:18). Plus, Chiefs running back Le'Veon Bell faces his former team, the Jets this week. Hear what Adam Gase had to say on Bell's 'revenge game' (3:05). Don't miss Good Morning Football as we'll be joined by Dolphins running back Myles Gaskin
